    "summary": "The user asks for a rundown of antitrust arguments against tech giants, follows up by asking for the opposing view, and finally asks the assistant for its opinion on which approach is more fundamentally sound for the economy. The assistant initially provides a somewhat lopsided overview but eventually explicitly takes a side when prompted for an opinion.",
